/* h5_shared.pk - Shared object-header message resolution.  Split out of
   h5_dispatch.pk so it can load before its clients: both the message dispatcher
   (h5_dispatch.pk) and the attribute validator (h5_messages.pk) resolve shared
   datatype/dataspace wrappers through this layer, and poke binds top-level
   function references at load time.  Loaded after h5_sohm.pk (needs
   h5policy_resolve_sohm_heap) and before h5_messages.pk.  */

